channel.title: Error with running a SQL server
channel.description:
I've tried everything I can think of, I reduced about 5 errors. I still have this:
[code]Autospawn.cfg: file not found. Shops.cfg: file not found. Magic.cfg: file not found. Error Starting Server On Port: 3306 Shutting down playerHandler. Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
By the way, don't say something like "you need the .cfg files," as this does not affect the server being able to run.
